column5: In 2009 the government will start locking up all the mentally ill.  I started crying when I thought of Greencoachdawg Run little buddy, run.
Oh heck!!! I thought this might be something I didn't know aboot... or that we all need to be "upwind" of you!
LOL Glenn, need a cell mate? I will answer to bubba! Bottom bunk for me, I don`t climb!
Man...this board is going to be dead next year.
Not at all,were just getting ready for the open water to take effect.LOL
mentally ill well i guess i'm going in since the wife always says that. Anyone need a room mate hahaha
You're right Brian...  I always consider fishing as my mental health therapy...and God knows I need it sometimes...

This man was walking by the "mental hospital" when he could hear this loud chanting....13....13....13.....13 So...he decides to take a peek through a hole he found in the fence...just then he gets poked in the eye with a stick!!! and what does he hear....14.....14.....14....14
